---
import Button from "./ui/button.astro";
---

<section class="md:w-[90vw] h-auto bg-[#F5F5DC] mx-auto rounded-2xl py-12 w-full xl:w-[80vw] transition-all">
  <h2
    class="text-[#2E7D32] text-center text-2xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold"
  >
    A Symphony of Premium Rice Varieties
  </h2>
  <p class="text-[#4B4B4B] text-center mx-auto text-base py-4 max-w-[55vw]">
    We source organic paddy directly from farmers, crafting premium rice and
    maize while repurposing husk by products into valuable products.
  </p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:w-[55vw] mx-auto md:gap-5 lg:gap-12 my-8">
    <div class="">
      <img src="rice-1.webp" alt="" class="md:rounded-tr-3xl md:rounded-bl-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="rice-2.webp" alt="" class="md:rounded-tr-3xl md:rounded-bl-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="rice-2.webp" alt="" class="md:rounded-tr-3xl md:rounded-bl-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="rice-1.webp" alt="" class="md:rounded-tr-3xl md:rounded-bl-3xl" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center my-8">
    <Button> Explore More</Button>
  </div>
</section>
